channel.description:

item.title: Compiler help
item.dc:creator: @LumbysChild LumbysChild
item.description:
@LumbysChild wrote:

[quote=“Sickdivison, post:1, topic:442738”]’“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\javac.exe”’ is not recognized as an inter
nal or external command,
operable program or batch file.
Press any key to continue . . .

Whats wrong???[/quote]

Go to My Computer\C:\Program Files\Java\

Should come up with…
C:\Program Files\Java\jre7\

Just make it…
C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre7\bin\javac.exe
or
C:\Program Files\Java\jre6\bin\javac.exe
